    dc:creator "Jameson, Mary Liz; Wada, Kaoru" ;
    dc:date "2009" ;
    dc:title "Five new species of Peltonotus Burmeister (Scarabaeidae: Dynastinae: Cyclocephalini) from Southeast Asia" ;
