<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5167891>
    dc:description "Figure 1-7. Peltonotus species dorsal habitus. 1) P. animus (holotype, male). 2) P. cybele (holotype, female). 3) P. favonius (holotype male). 4) P. karubei (male paratype). 5) P. karubei (male) showing variation. 6) P. mushiyaus (holotype female). 7) P. tigerus (holotype female). Scale bar = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5167891/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5167893>
    dc:description "Figure 8-13. Maxilla (dorsal view) showing mala with or without lamellate setal brush (black arrow) and form. 8) P. animus (holotype). 9) P. cybele (holotype). 10) P. favonius (holotype). 11) P. karubei. 12) P. mushiyaus (holotype). 13) P. tigerus (holotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5167893/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5167895>
    dc:description "Figure 14-18. Male genitalia in dorsal and left lateral view. 14a-b) P. karubei. 15a-b) P. favonius (holotype). 16ab) P. malayensis. 17a-b) P. animus (holotype). 18a-b) P. silvanus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5167895/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5167901>
    dc:description "Figure 25. Distribution of Peltonotus species in Southeast Asia and Sundaland." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5167901/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

